         sibling-merge path in PomlessMojo.writeRulesXmlDeps must look the name up via the reactor's
         rules.xml — not infer it from the artifactId. -->
    <name>Clean Leaf Domain</name>
    <modules>
        <module>
            <rules-root path="rules/*.xlsx"/>
        </module>
    </modules>
</project>
